-- my-blog project using php and mysql--
This project have a one login system that accept three user base on their role.. 
(1) Super-admin: The super-admin is the overall user that have access to delete, add, and update user data.
Also create, delete, update posts. Which role is 2
(2) Admin : The admin can create post. But can not delete and update posts. which role is 1
(3)Normal user : Which role is 0 have access only to the index page where they can read post that was add by admin nor superadmin

